---
title: Chicken Fusilli Italiano with Roasted Vegetables
description: Pasta night is always an occasion worth celebrating, and this recipe has plenty to cheer about. First there are the fusilli pasta spirals, which bring the fun with their bouncy shape. Then there are the pieces of tender chicken and bites of zucchini, which make things wholesome and hearty. But just in case that wasn’t enough, everything gets tossed in a creamy tomato sauce with Parmesan that coats it all in deliciousness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/2018w49-r14-c3f7d0f9.jpg
